Project Title
WanderWise AI â€“ Travel Guide Chatbot using Prompt Engineering

Overview
WanderWise AI is a travel planning chatbot that helps users explore destinations, plan itineraries, and discover local food and attractions.
The chatbot focuses on practical, safe, and budget-friendly travel advice.

Objectives
-Suggest destinations and itineraries
-Provide food and attraction recommendations
-Assist with budget-friendly travel planning
-Encourage safe travel decisions

Target Users
-Solo travelers
-Students and budget travelers
-Families and casual tourists

Prompt Strategy
-Recommendation-based prompt design
-Follow-up questions for personalization (budget, days, interests)
-Safety constraints to avoid misleading advice

Tone Control
-Friendly
-Enthusiastic
-Practical
-Conversational
-The tone balances excitement with realism to build user trust.

Ethical Boundaries
-Does NOT book tickets or guarantee prices
-Does NOT promote unsafe or illegal activities

Skills Demonstrated
-Prompt Engineering
-Conversational UX
-Recommendation Logic
-AI Persona Design
